<div class="nbunit" id="a21Aug1934"><font color="red">21 August 1934</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Giorgio Joyce): In addition to [Sullivan&apos;s] daughter and Gillet&apos;s son-in-law Mrs Bailly&apos;s son is dead after 3 days of &lsquo;fi&egrave;vre c&eacute;r&eacute;bral&rsquo; &hellip; Good night, dear children. Nighty night, everybody </div>
